title: League not working when pressing 'Launch' button in Client
body:
Ever since I got my custom PC, League hasn't been working for me and it's really irritating. I'm able to open the client, but when I press 'Launch', nothing seems to happen.
I have - reinstalled 3 times
- restarted my PC 
- Go on C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\ and launched "lol,launcher.admin.exe"
- C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\RADS\Projects\lol_air_client\releases\0.0.1.198\deploy\ and run "LolClient.exe" 
but that still doesn't work. 
Can someone please assist me?

replies.body:
Hey there,

Could you please download the [Hextech Toolkit](https://s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/player-support/tools/HTK_Setup.msi) for me, install it and run, select your region and click run.

A file should be saved to your desktop called **LoL-Logs.zip** please upload this file somewhere (mega.co.nz preferably) and reply with a link here.
I'm trying to upload it onto mega.co.nz  but it is not working
Feel free to upload the file anywhere you'd like.
